original: Zetterlund, Carl Gustaf, fängelsedirektör, Göteborg, f. 22/1/87 i Härnösand av fabr. Gustaf Z. o. Karin Nordlund. G. 18 m. Beda Katarina Sandman. Barn: Ylva f. 19, fil. mag., Göran 20, soc. stud. — Stud:ex., resoff:-ex., jur. stud. v. Upps. univ. Kapten i Västmanl. reg. res. Dir. f. stat. vård-anst. i Venngarn 24, v. centr:fäng. i Härnösand 30, v. centr:fäng. å Här-landa fr. 41.
translated: Zetterlund, Carl Gustaf, prison director, Gothenburg, b. 22/1/87 in Härnösand, son of fabricator Gustaf Z. and Karin Nordlund. Married in 1918 to Beda Katarina Sandman. Children: Ylva, b. 1919, holds a master's degree in philosophy, Göran, b. 1920, studying sociology. Completed secondary school exams, reserve officer exams, and studied law at Uppsala University. Captain in the Västmanland Regiment reserve. Director of the state care institution in Venngarn from 1924, the central prison in Härnösand from 1930, and the central prison in Härlanda from 1941.
